Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.8
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: PhoneAura is a free, modern redesign of the iOS 16 Phone app. Enjoy elegant custom Favorites, smart Recents filters, detailed call information, redesigned Contacts and Keypad, swipe-to-delete controls, custom favorite contacts, haptic feedback, fluid animations, and clean Next Solution settings. Built for rootless jailbreaks.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
